Text: Welcome to DisneyStorecomJoseph Stepenovitch Welcome to DisneyStorecom Here is everything you need to start enjoying all of your DisneyStorecom and GO Network member benefits WHATS MY MEMBER NAME AND PASSWORD Your Member Name is jstepeno If youve forgotten your password just click on or go to scriptsGoAccountManagerrequestdllsendPassword Here are step by step instructions to help you get started once you activate your Membership How to Log In How to Take Advantage of Your DisneyStorecom Member Benefits How to Log In Just go to DisneyStorecom click on Log In at the top of the page then type in your Member Name and password in the appropriate fields How to Take Advantage of Your DisneyStorecom Member Benefits Once logged in you can access all of our member services by clicking on the Account Info button at the top of the page There you will be able to update your member profile build your address book and track your complete order history In addition to these services registered members will always get the inside scoop on special deals and promotions at the store Well be adding even more member services and benefits in the near future so make sure to check in with us early and often WHAT IS THE GO NETWORK The GO Network is an exciting partnership between Infoseek and The Walt Disney Company that brings together great sites like ESPNcom ABCNewscom ABCcom and Disneycom and adds the power of Infoseeks search and directory tools The goal To make your life easier by making the Internet work for you Check out what GO Network can do for you Open your FREE GO Network email account at Start a FREE home page with virtually unlimited storage at Personalize the GO Network home page with the news weather sports scores horoscope lottery and tools you like best at Try our powerful search and directory services with the GOguardianTM cleansearch option for families at Take part in chats and other community services at Community Play FREE classic games and chat with others while playing at CenterGamesPlayClassic games Best of all its easy You can use the same Member Name and password at all GO Network sites MEMBERSHIP ASSISTANCE If you need further assistance please click on the GOcom Help Index at HelphelphtmlkeyHELPTINDEX or send an email with your questions or comments to And again welcome to Disney Store Online and the GO Network Sincerely Margaret Davis GO Network Member Services PS If this account was set up in error or you received this email in error please click here to deactivate the account automatically scriptsvrdllvnCABDADEACEE D
